<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <head>
        <title>Citation Manager</title>
       <style type="text/css">  
          body {font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif}        
       </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Citation Manager</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the Citation Manager.  This demo uses w3c XForms and has been tested with FireFox 2.0 with the XForms addon.</p>
        <p>This demo allows you to manipulate Items using XForms and eXist using basic database operations CRUD (Create, Read/Search, Update, Delete) operations:
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <a href="views/list-items.xq">List</a> List of all Citations
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="edit/edit.xq?new=true">New</a> Create New Citations
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="search/search.xhtml">Search</a> Search Citations
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="views/list-categories.xq">View Citations by Category</a>List  all citations by classification
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="views/list-categories.xq">View Citation Tags</a>List all citation tags
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="views/metrics.xq">Citation Metrics</a> Counts of various citation metrics
                </li>
            </ol>
        </p>
    </body>
</html>